The present invention will be described below with reference to the accompanying drawings, wherein:


FIGS. 1-4 show the various stages of synchronization in a three-node SONET ring network without the use of the present invention;


FIGS. 5-8 show the various stages of synchronization in a three-node ring SONET network using the present invention;


FIGS. 9-13 show the various stages of synchronization in a three node linear SONET network without the use of the present invention;


FIGS. 14-18 show the various stages of synchronization in a three node linear SONET network using the present invention;


